Subject: [PATCH 0947/4530] drm/amd/display: Use dcn1 Optimal Taps Get

[WHY]
dpp2_get_optimal_number_of_taps is incorrect, and dcn2 should be using
dpp1_get_optimal_number_of_taps instead

